item.title: Carl Brown Guitar Lessons
item.description: This channel by Carl Brown contains theory and technique lessons for playing the guitar.

item.title: Katie DeNure Ukulele Lessons
item.description: Katie DeNure is a music teacher at One Music School which offers private Guitar, Voice, and Ukulele lessons online via Skype.

item.title: Steve Stine Guitar Channel
item.description: The channel of guitarist and teacher Steve Stine features lessons on music theory, guitar technique as well as riff and song tutorials with a good dose of heavy metal music.

item.title: YourGuitarSage: Tutorials, Technique, Theory and Exercises
item.description: The channel of professional guitarist and teacher Erich Andreas with song tutorials, technique, theory and exercises mainly for guitar and some ukulele.

item.title: Drue James: Acoustic Guitar Lessons
item.description: Drue James teaches acoustic and fingerstyle guitar lessons for beginner and intermediate players.

item.title: GuitarMadeEZ: Guitar Lessons
item.description: A channel with the goal to teach how to play guitar the EZ way by a self-taught guitarist who has been playing for 17 years.

item.title: Cynthia Lin Ukulele Lessons
item.description: Cynthia Lin is a modern day jazz ukulele diva based in San Francisco, California, who teaches how to play the ukulele in engaging tutorials on YouTube.

item.title: Guitarhabits: Guitar Lessons
item.description: Guitar Habits's channel with guitar lessons about practicing, rhythm, soloing, performing, songwriting, gear, improving skills, lifestyle and motivation.

item.title: Guitareo Guitar Lessons
item.description: The guitar lessons on this channel are designed to help new students get started or experienced guitarists take their playing to the next level.

item.title: The Ukulele Teacher: Ukulele Lessons and Songs
item.description: A great channel for beginners and intermediate Ukulele players with hundreds of lessons teaching popular songs.
